<div class="title">A Sacred Cord</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=InnerVenus&Exact=1">InnerVenus</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; InnerVenus. "A Sacred Cord: An Experience with AMT (exp97313)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 19, 2016. erowid.org/exp/97313</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
